Mobileye Logo
Mobileye is an Israeli subsidiary of Intel that develops self-driving cars and advanced driver-assistance systems. Mobileye headquarters and main Research & Development centre is located in Jerusalem operating under the company name Mobileye Vision Technology Ltd. The company also has sales and marketing offices in Midtown, Manhattan, US; Shanghai, China; Tokyo, Japan and Düsseldorf, Germany. In March 2017, Intel announced that they had agreed to a US$15.3 billion takeover of Mobileye.
